by our friends and brethren.

275
00:20:35,625 --> 00:20:38,583
Under the banner of Inferno.

276
00:20:38,666 --> 00:20:40,041
Splendid!

277
00:20:40,125 --> 00:20:41,416
It's a miracle,

278
00:20:41,500 --> 00:20:44,416
and we can attribute it all
to your Phantom.

279
00:20:44,500 --> 00:20:46,625
Pleased to be of service.

