Lieutenant Cyrus Gant,
received an award

281
00:20:52,958 --> 00:20:55,500
from the Mayor earlier today
for his contribution

282
00:20:55,583 --> 00:20:57,916
in resolving the mafia war,

283
00:20:58,000 --> 00:21:00,750
a conflict that shook
the heart of this city.

284
00:21:00,833 --> 00:21:03,958
Melanie Square entrepreneur
and gang leader, Tony Stone,

285
00:21:04,041 --> 00:21:05,208
was behind...

