to those men?

288
00:21:10,250 --> 00:21:13,333
You'll find people don't really
care about the truth.

289
00:21:13,416 --> 00:21:15,250
They're not even interested.

290
00:21:15,333 --> 00:21:16,500
...was brought to an end

291
00:21:16,583 --> 00:21:19,333
by Lt. Gant's heroic actions.

292
00:21:33,041 --> 00:21:34,458
I wonder
if anyone will pray

293
00:21:34,541 --> 00:21:36,625
for the people
that died that day.

