prayer nor atonement.

296
00:21:44,583 --> 00:21:46,833
Death is the end
of everything.

297
00:21:46,916 --> 00:21:48,916
It doesn't matter
what you do after that.

298
00:21:51,125 --> 00:21:52,625
There's no point.

